<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/visitbritain> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "VisitBritain (VB) is the national tourism agency, responsible for marketing Britain worldwide and developing Britain’s visitor economy. It works with UK Trade & Investment as well as airlines, travel operators, global brands and the official tourism bodies for London, England, Scotland and Wales. VB is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ."@en .
